 real-stable (equivalently,\nLorentzian, or strongly/completely log-concave), if and only if the\nnormalization of $p_G(-{\\bf n})$ is strongly Rayleigh.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 17:50:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 17:29:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 04:59:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
