 to a full 3D model. The effect is\nubiquitous, since surfactant is present in many technical and natural dewetting\nprocesses either deliberately or as contamination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 07:16:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 18:31:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-05"}
