tries that will be formed during\nwar. Also, we have visually depicted the number of communities that will be\nformed in this war and the participating countries in each communities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 10:38:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 18 Jul 2021 05:44:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 22 Aug 2021 05:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2021 04:49:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-08"}
