 mass (presumably BH mass) ranging from several hundred\nto above $10^5 M_\\odot$, potentially forming massive BH binary mergers and\nyielding gravitational wave events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 May 2021 15:53:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 15:25:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
